sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant C as ETH / SOL Watcher
    participant F as Federation (t-of-n)
    participant R as BTH Reserve

    U->>C: Burn wBTH
    C->>C: Confirm (depth window / Finalized)
    C->>F: Confirmed burn
    F->>F: Collect t-of-n release attestation<br/>(order-bound)
    F->>R: Release reserve BTH
    R->>R: Release to fresh stealth address
    Note over R: Target-state: tag 100% to epoch<br/>import cluster c_import(m)<br/>at import_factor(m) >= F
    Note over R: Live (register row IMP-2):<br/>releases a factor-1 output
    R-->>U: BTH received
